<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 22:05:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普的封口费案刑事审判开始</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-faces-criminal-trial-in-new-york-courtroom/articleshow/109322953.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109322953.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特朗普在曼哈顿面临刑事审判，他批评白宫领导层，并在陪审团遴选过程中强调他的 2024 年总统候选人资格，陪审团遴选将持续两周。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 18:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-faces-criminal-trial-in-new-york-courtroom/articleshow/109322953.cms</guid></item><item><title>弗朗西斯·斯科特基大桥倒塌：联邦调查局对巴尔的摩桥梁倒塌事件展开刑事调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/francis-scott-key-bridge-collapse-fbi-opens-criminal-probe-into-baltimores-bridge-collapse/articleshow/109317046.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109317046.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联邦调查局目前正在调查巴尔的摩弗朗西斯·斯科特基桥的悲惨倒塌事件，重点关注导致事故发生的情况，并确定是否遵守所有联邦法律。​​​调查是在“大理”号货轮上进行的，是由一位不愿透露姓名的消息人士向美联社透露的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/francis-scott-key-bridge-collapse-fbi-opens-criminal-probe-into-baltimores-bridge-collapse/articleshow/109317046.cms</guid></item><item><title>先进的“DragonFire”激光器可能会改变乌克兰对俄罗斯的战争战略</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/advanced-dragonfire-laser-could-transform-ukraines-war-strategy-against-russia/articleshow/109321216.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109321216.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于乌克兰仍然顽固地防御俄罗斯的长期入侵，它正处于可能获得英国先进的“龙火”高功率激光武器原型的边缘。经过七年多的开发，该武器在最近的测试中展示了其精度，标志着两国军事技术的重大进步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/advanced-dragonfire-laser-could-transform-ukraines-war-strategy-against-russia/articleshow/109321216.cms</guid></item><item><title>“芝加哥活动人士因伊朗袭击以色列而爆发欢呼”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/activists-in-chicago-erupt-in-cheers-over-irans-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109321233.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109321233.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在芝加哥，一群自称为反战活动人士的人在听到伊朗导弹和无人机袭击以色列的消息后欢呼雀跃。这一事件发生在“March On DNC 2024”和“Anti War Chicago”团体的一次会议期间。据军方报告称，周六晚上，伊朗向以色列领土发射了 300 多枚导弹和无人机，这些导弹和无人机主要被以色列及其盟国拦截。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:22:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/activists-in-chicago-erupt-in-cheers-over-irans-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109321233.cms</guid></item><item><title>堪萨斯州妇女失踪案，四人被捕，俄克拉荷马州农村发现两具尸体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-bodies-found-in-rural-oklahoma-after-4-arrested-in-case-of-missing-kansas-women/articleshow/109320117.cms</link><description>与绑架和谋杀两名堪萨斯州妇女有关的四人被捕后，俄克拉荷马州农村地区发现了两具尸体。来自堪萨斯州雨果顿的 27 岁维罗妮卡·巴特勒 (Veronica Butler) 和 39 岁吉利安·凯利 (Jilian Kelley) 正准备去接巴特勒的孩子参加生日聚会，但从未抵达。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 14:54:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-bodies-found-in-rural-oklahoma-after-4-arrested-in-case-of-missing-kansas-women/articleshow/109320117.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊姆兰·汗指控妻子“中毒”后，布什拉·比比向高等法院寻求医疗检查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/bushra-bibi-moves-high-court-seeks-medical-examination-after-imran-khan-alleges-wife-being-poisoned/articleshow/109317050.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109317050.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;布什拉·比比 (Bushra Bibi) 涉嫌中毒后前往肖卡特·卡努姆 (Shaukat Khanum) 医院接受体检。伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 的 PTI 要求进行考试。没有发现中毒证据。 Bibi 出现胃痛、食欲异常和舌苔。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/bushra-bibi-moves-high-court-seeks-medical-examination-after-imran-khan-alleges-wife-being-poisoned/articleshow/109317050.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦当局宣布西南部进入紧急状态，闪电和降雨造成 41 人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-lightning-rains-kill-people-in-pakistan-as-authorities-declare-a-state-of-emergency-in-southwest/articleshow/109316487.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109316487.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;官员周一表示，过去三天，巴基斯坦西南部当局宣布进入紧急状态，闪电和暴雨已造成巴基斯坦各地至少 36 人死亡，其中大部分是农民。阿尔凡·卡蒂亚说，大多数死亡事件是由于雷击击中旁遮普省东部收割小麦的农民以及降雨导致房屋倒塌而造成的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-lightning-rains-kill-people-in-pakistan-as-authorities-declare-a-state-of-emergency-in-southwest/articleshow/109316487.cms</guid></item><item><title>高科技防御：以色列如何“迷惑”伊朗无人机和导弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/high-tech-defense-how-israel-managed-to-confuse-iranian-drones-and-missiles/articleshow/109311061.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109311061.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/high-tech-defense-how-israel-managed-to-confuse-iranian-drones-and-missiles/articleshow/109311061.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对以色列的袭击引发了避免全面战争的竞赛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-attack-on-israel-sparks-race-to-avert-a-full-blown-war/articleshow/109310471.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109310471.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-attack-on-israel-sparks-race-to-avert-a-full-blown-war/articleshow/109310471.cms</guid></item><item><title>苹果否认在 Epic Games 诉讼中违反美国法院命令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/apple-denies-violating-us-court-order-in-epic-games-lawsuit/articleshow/109310260.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109310260.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;苹果驳斥了有关其 App Store 违抗法院命令的指控，并请求加州联邦法官驳回 Epic Games 藐视法庭的请求。这家科技巨头在向美国地区法官伊冯·冈萨雷斯·罗杰斯 (Yvonne Gonzalez Rogers) 提交的文件中捍卫了自己的立场，后者负责监督 Epic 2020 年指控苹果违反反垄断法的诉讼。在围绕应用程序分发和应用内支付法规的法律斗争正在进行中，苹果公司的立场仍然坚定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:25:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/apple-denies-violating-us-court-order-in-epic-games-lawsuit/articleshow/109310260.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯表示对中东紧张局势升级极为担忧并敦促克制</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-says-its-extremely-concerned-by-rise-in-middle-east-tensions-urges-restraint/articleshow/109309926.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109309926.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯对伊朗袭击以色列后中东紧张局势感到担忧，并敦促克制和政治解决。克里姆林宫发言人表示，重大分歧只能通过政治和外交手段解决。伊朗采取行动是对大使馆袭击的回应。俄罗斯避免批评伊朗。加沙战争导致紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-says-its-extremely-concerned-by-rise-in-middle-east-tensions-urges-restraint/articleshow/109309926.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国对维权人士家属进行“集体惩罚”：人权组织</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-using-collective-punishment-against-activists-families-rights-group/articleshow/109309585.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109309585.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据一个人权组织周一发出的警报，在对民间社会不断升级的打压中，中国人权活动人士的后代正面临着父母倡导的影响。中国经常被指责在新疆、西藏以及现在的香港压制人权。北京反驳了这些说法，将其归咎于对其进步的抹黑运动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-using-collective-punishment-against-activists-families-rights-group/articleshow/109309585.cms</guid></item><item><title>新加坡总理李显龙下台； 5月15日将权力移交给继任者黄</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-pm-lee-steps-down-to-hand-over-power-to-successor-wong-on-may-15/articleshow/109308126.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109308126.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:21:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-pm-lee-steps-down-to-hand-over-power-to-successor-wong-on-may-15/articleshow/109308126.cms</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨向中国学生保证，我们在德国并不都吸大麻</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/we-dont-all-smoke-weed-in-germany-scholz-assures-chinese-students/articleshow/109308323.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109308323.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;肖尔茨是在回答同济大学一名学生的提问时发表上述言论的。该学生询问，如果他在德国学习，是否必须吸食大麻，因为这种药物在中国并不合法。德国二月份通过了大麻合法化立法，允许个人和协会种植和拥有有限数量的大麻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:25:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/we-dont-all-smoke-weed-in-germany-scholz-assures-chinese-students/articleshow/109308323.cms</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列战时内阁将于格林威治标准时间 1100 点重新召开会议，应对伊朗对峙</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-war-cabinet-to-reconvene-at-1100-gmt-in-iran-standoff-source-says/articleshow/109307986.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109307986.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:15:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-war-cabinet-to-reconvene-at-1100-gmt-in-iran-standoff-source-says/articleshow/109307986.cms</guid></item><item><title>越来越多的德国市长想辞职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/more-and-more-german-mayors-want-to-quit/articleshow/109304877.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109304877.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国总统施泰因迈尔强调德国当地政客面临的日益严重的危险，强调了右翼极端主义的威胁、袭击和担忧。调查显示，40% 的小镇市长和 57% 的民选官员遭受过侮辱和人身攻击。挑战包括网上的敌意和对政治捐款的怀疑。这些举措旨在支持和保护市政代表。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 07:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/more-and-more-german-mayors-want-to-quit/articleshow/109304877.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦燃油价格可能达到每升8.50巴基斯坦卢比</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/fuel-prices-in-pakistan-likely-to-hit-pkr-8-50-per-litre/articleshow/109303425.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109303425.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据《黎明报》报道，随着中东局势继续发展，国际市场走高预计将推高汽油和高速柴油价格，分别约为每升2.50巴基斯坦卢比和8.50巴基斯坦卢比。据消息人士透露，在近期升级之前的过去两周内，汽油和高速柴油 (HSD) 价格分别上涨了约 4 美元/桶和 4.50 美元/桶。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/fuel-prices-in-pakistan-likely-to-hit-pkr-8-50-per-litre/articleshow/109303425.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗山洪造成至少33人死亡、27人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/at-least-33-killed-27-injured-in-flash-floods-in-afghanistan/articleshow/109304482.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109304482.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据 TOLOnews 报道，过去三天降雪、下雨和随后的洪水对该国造成严重破坏，造成至少 33 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/at-least-33-killed-27-injured-in-flash-floods-in-afghanistan/articleshow/109304482.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国大选：特朗普若被定罪还能当总统吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-election-can-trump-still-become-president-if-convicted/articleshow/109304134.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109304134.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2024 年 11 月美国总统大选的共和党推定候选人唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对法庭并不陌生。 2024 年 1 月，纽约陪审团裁定，他必须向作家 E·让·卡罗尔支付数百万美元的赔偿金，原因是对她进行性虐待，然后诽谤特朗普，特朗普正在对这一决定提出上诉。那是一起民事案件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-election-can-trump-still-become-president-if-convicted/articleshow/109304134.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：伊姆兰·汗政党领导人表示，谢里夫家族“害怕”804号囚犯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-sharif-family-afraid-of-prisoner-number-804-says-leader-of-imran-khans-party/articleshow/109300503.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109300503.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周日，国民议会反对党领袖奥马尔·阿尤布在奎达向媒体发表讲话时表示，谢里夫家族“害怕”804号囚犯，指的是巴基斯坦正义运动（PTI）主席伊姆兰·汗的囚犯编号。 。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-sharif-family-afraid-of-prisoner-number-804-says-leader-of-imran-khans-party/articleshow/109300503.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>